                  </hi>. I live in South Molton-street—Maley gave me information in St. Paul's Churchyard, and I missed my handkerchief—I had used it within half-an-hour—I have one of the same pattern with me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> As I was standing in St. Paul's Church-yard, the policeman collared me; he did not say any thing; I <hi rend="italic">shoved</hi> him away; he then told me the charge; and while I was talking to him, a young man made off with the gentleman's handkerchief. <hi rend="largeCaps">

